(I believe Mach 1 is 331.9 -  344.4 meters per second, Mach 1 is the speed of 
sound, but the thing I checked said sound travelled faster in warmer 
temperatures, but I don't it has the same effect for a plane.  And no one was 
heading for space)


Unitron/Firestarter:



Unitron could feel a slight pain inside himself as he flew, changing course 
at seeing shots strike the Maximal bridge.  "Meet me at the bridge." he said 
via inner monologue comm. to Firestarter.  He powered up his lasers and 
missiles, and armed some flares.  No doubt those fools would try and harm him 
again.  If they damaged his fastest mode, they would be one with the Void.


---

"Understood." he replied in the same fashion of comm.  He was nearly braking 
the sound barrier, but he began to slow so he could make a good enough turn 
for the bridge.  He flew under any missile tubes in the side of the CF so he 
wouldn't be shot at.
